      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find for any discerning buyer. It has been meticulously cared for, featuring a flawless exterior with no scratches, chips, or dents, and an interior that remains in pristine, like-new condition. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been maintained to the highest standards with a complete service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
